<Schematic Name="Fuzz Face (PNP positive-ground)" Description="Two-PNP-transistor fuzz with positive ground — the classic PNP Fuzz Face topology. Battery negative is the &quot;V-&quot; rail (-9V relative to chassis ground). Uses 2N3906/2N5087 (silicon PNP substitutes for AC128 germaniums)." PartNumber="">
